#. type: Plain text
#: src/cultivons/DESCRIPTION.md:2
msgid ""
"__Cultivons!__ is a software in the form of an internal site aiming at "
"helping the management of a BAD (Sustainable Autonomous Base)."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: src/cultivons/DESCRIPTION.md:4
msgid ""
"A BAD is a place where one or more people can (over)live a disaster "
"(natural, plague, war, economic collapse ... put here the reason that "
"pleases you or scares you the most), for a more or less long period of time, "
"without needing the outside: supermarkets, hospitals, and other services "
"present in a modern society."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: src/cultivons/DESCRIPTION.md:6
msgid ""
"This definition is a little broad, in fact a BAD will often materialize by a "
"place in the countryside where one will try to be as autonomous as possible "
"on the most important aspects of survival:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: src/cultivons/DESCRIPTION.md:13
msgid ""
"food (vegetable garden, orchard, animals... everything that is culture and "
"breeding);"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: src/cultivons/DESCRIPTION.md:13
msgid "electricity;"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: src/cultivons/DESCRIPTION.md:13
msgid "water (including potabilization);"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: src/cultivons/DESCRIPTION.md:13
msgid "heating;"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: src/cultivons/DESCRIPTION.md:13
msgid "first aid;"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: src/cultivons/DESCRIPTION.md:13
msgid "storage of recipes, guides and other documentation..."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: src/cultivons/DESCRIPTION.md:20
msgid ""
"With __cultivons!__, you can manage - your crops, your garden and the "
"associated tasks (semi, harvest) as well as garden plan.  - the weather, - "
"the stocks, - your documents, - your budget (Bank Account)."
msgstr ""

